@7134=~Dandy Loafers~
@7135=~Unlike typical adventurer fare, these shoes are designed with comfort first in mind. They are inlaid with the softest fur and wool and make ones feet feel as if they are stepping on clouds when wearing them. An exquisite comfort for even the most scrutinizing dandy. While such loafers should fall apart on a long journey, a clever enchantment keeps them in good condition and they even seem to clean themselves overnight. 

Even more valuable however are a twinned set of enchantments that keep their wearer safe; one for speed and one for protection. These ensure that the wearer lives to enjoy another quiet night by the fire with their feet raised high, basking in the comfort of their loafers.

However, the sophistication of the enchantment also extends to rejecting being worn by those whose feet are unsuitably rough and 'peasantly' to appreciate them. As such, more martially inclined folk may find them simply a pair of comfortable if opinionated shoes.

Usable by: Bard, Mage, Mage-Thief

